[div class=p 
	"Crossroad Circuit has dash plates all over the place. This means slowing down for rival bumps is basically not worth it. Additionally I was often able to avoid going out of my way to get boosts from other spawns because a nearby dash plate would just refill my speed anyways.
	$LF
