	"On most boost laps, I used it at the start because that’s where there’s the longest duration between dash plates. However, at the end of lap 4 I got a mine that allowed me to carry a lot of speed into the start of lap 5. Combined with some decent spawns, I was able to save my boost for after the hairpin.
	$LF
]div
